{"tid":2220183,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我真係好自卑","createTime":"2020-09-27T12:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:29:19.000Z","uid":376118,"like":67,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c6624cab64977da93167c0926cd8b7d7a4455465","tid":2220183,"uid":376118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:47:09.000Z","msg":"「家庭」<br />\n細個屋企好窮<br />\n依家都好窮<br />\n雖然父母並不能給我十分富裕的生活<br />\n時不時都有嗌交<br />\n但都算和諧<br />\n都感謝屋企人對我的支持<br />\n<br />\n「學業」<br />\n讀左一間普普通通既大學<br />\n成績一般<br />\n個樣一般<br />\n好多事情都係一般般<br />\n<br />\n「事業」<br />\n出來做野一年<br />\n身邊的同事都係有錢人<br />\n討論的話題 衫褲鞋 我都搭唔上一句<br />\n形成一種無形的差距<br />\n好自卑<br />\n<br />\n「感情」<br />\n最近又分左手<br />\n算是異地男朋友<br />\n陸續拍左一年<br />\n其實只是拍左前3個月<br />\n後9個月都冇見面<br />\n但佢講既分手<br />\n好難過<br />\n覺得自己好冇用<br />\n點解一拍拖就散<br />\n所以我好自卑<br />\n<br />\n依家27歲<br />\n好困惑的年紀"},{"pid":"b4fa71956d8feaecfbe8fc95832cd42157e6bc8d","tid":2220183,"uid":55458,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:48:43.000Z","msg":"Pmed <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b647dc11976ac9ba9aa0db7721562f367ea92478","tid":2220183,"uid":38904,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"自己活得開心咪得<br />\n使乜同人比較"},{"pid":"b2f0fb74b120e47a15365841719c1cc858b5921d","tid":2220183,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"我都好窮<br />\n<br />\n不過見身邊好多叻人都住劏房<br />\n<br />\n就知社會問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太遲出生問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個政府玩死後生<br />\n<br />\n利申廢老<br />\n<br />\n以前廢老都有公屋住  <br />\n<br />\n而家你大學生搵d普通工生活仲衰過廢老"},{"pid":"4446b17e5a28a3578f3c7838abf6ee23e0ef2c8c","tid":2220183,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20